    public class JobState
extends SourceState
    A class for tracking job state information.

      static class  JobState.DatasetState
      A subclass of JobState that is used to represent dataset states.

      An enumeration of possible job states, which are identical to WorkUnitState.WorkingState in terms of naming.

      • createDatasetStatesByUrns

        public Map<String,JobState.DatasetState> createDatasetStatesByUrns()
        Create a Map from dataset URNs (as being specified by ConfigurationKeys.DATASET_URN_KEY to JobState.DatasetState objects that represent the dataset states and store TaskStates corresponding to the datasets.

        TaskStates that do not have ConfigurationKeys.DATASET_URN_KEY set will be added to the dataset state belonging to ConfigurationKeys.DEFAULT_DATASET_URN.

        Returns:
        a Map from dataset URNs to JobState.DatasetStates representing the dataset states
